name: Reuniting With My Family and Girlfriend After 2 Years
description:
MY BROTHER IS HOME!! üò≠‚úàÔ∏è Emotional Missionary Homecoming After 2 Years

After two years away, Brock is finally HOME!! He spent the last year and a half serving in Boston, Massachusetts, and this vlog captures the unforgettable moments leading up to his return. From packing his (very heavy) bags and saying goodbye to mission friends, to getting paired with a final companion‚Äîhis journey back was emotional and full of meaning.

Back at home, I was getting everything ready for his arrival‚Äîstocking the pantry (per Brock‚Äôs special request), grabbing some of his favorite foods, and prepping the house for a big surprise. We stayed up late making posters (yes, including a hilarious ‚Äúmarry me‚Äù one and some Fortnite-themed signs üòÇ) and decorated everything to make his homecoming extra special.

He landed in Salt Lake City, and the moment he walked through those airport doors‚Ä¶ we were all in tears. Our mom cried, and the biggest surprise of all‚Äîhis girlfriend was there to meet him even though he thought she‚Äôd still be out of town üëÄ

Once we got home, Brock saw his room for the first time, opened his welcome-back gift basket, and we wrapped up the perfect day with a Bees baseball game as a family. It was one of those days we‚Äôll never forget.

name: We Spent 48 Hours With MLB All-Stars!
description:
We Spent 2 Days with MLB All-Stars at the 95th All-Star Game in Atlanta, Georgia! We hope you enjoy this video and consider subscribing if you do, it really helps us out! ü¶æ

We‚Äôve got an action packed video this week as we attended the Home Run Derby and All-Star Game, along with media day and the red carpet show.
